{"tid":1459061,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［連登有愛］11號尖沙咀發夢的鐘麗娟小姐麻煩入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T18:30:45.000Z","uid":10426,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"34e810872b0eadcb46dd828195a09a4db7c0362a","tid":1459061,"uid":10426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZeroTKS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZeroTKS.png&h=f20ff6d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，昨日尖沙咀兵荒馬亂，我朋友出咗去發夢，係尖沙咀東某個公園走嘅過程途中見到個女仔跌咗張八達通卡，拎起準備比返佢嗰時，個女仔已經跑走左。<br />\n<br />\n鐘小姐，如果你想攞返張八達通卡，見到呢個post可以喺入面留言或者直接tg我，叫我朋友俾返你。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/rainbowisrising\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frainbowisrising&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB27P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=e6db56c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rainbowisrising</a><br />\n<br />\n如果明天十二點前，冇人認領，我哋就會交返畀地鐵公司，或者用其他方法銷毀佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到張相好似係中學生，知道大家最近買gear 冇買到冇晒錢，八達通幾十蚊都係錢，所以上嚟碰碰運氣，希望可以搵返佢主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0770b99e017482b916a13346c34d64df30d0712d","tid":1459061,"uid":10426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:57:39.000Z","msg":"自推一下 黑警死全家"},{"pid":"a4886ef893005c88c922737b997ed17c9b5ec61a","tid":1459061,"uid":10426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"自推到十連"},{"pid":"910487e6abdda9540d381d4aaaa11bc9080d7f26","tid":1459061,"uid":10426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"推到真人入來"},{"pid":"89cbbc693116638be8fe0e163a7b283d39b7ffb6","tid":1459061,"uid":254879,"l